    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel Quest: Guild 是一个放置类 RPG，设计为位于屏幕底部，在城镇中雇佣和升级英雄，当你准备好时，带他们去战斗，战斗会自动进行，每击败一个怪物，他们会掉落灵魂，摧毁水晶并进入下一阶段，使用这些灵魂进一步升级你的建筑和英雄，并尝试击败老板！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/d5984e50596ca0582fa6af75950f7164.poster.avif?t=1729304224\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/d5984e50596ca0582fa6af75950f7164.webm?t=1729304224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/d5984e50596ca0582fa6af75950f7164.mp4?t=1729304224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/b0c761b73b290ec18de8acc432d29ede.poster.avif?t=1729304224\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/b0c761b73b290ec18de8acc432d29ede.webm?t=1729304224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/b0c761b73b290ec18de8acc432d29ede.mp4?t=1729304224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/fefd746ad6e49637417f1a15442f9e2f.poster.avif?t=1729304224\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/fefd746ad6e49637417f1a15442f9e2f.webm?t=1729304224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/fefd746ad6e49637417f1a15442f9e2f.mp4?t=1729304224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >机制</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >声望系统：通过击败特定的老板获得奖牌，使用这些奖牌进一步提升你的英雄，或购买一些独特奖励的神器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发展你自己的公会，升级每个建筑以解锁新资源</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英雄在自动战斗中获得经验，所以在你做其他事情时让他们战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雇佣英雄的被动技能和主动技能的数百种组合</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss 战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照你想要的方式组建你的英雄队伍，尝试建立一个平衡的队伍或只是直接攻击水晶的盗贼！</p></li></ul>",
